{"tid":1168843,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足一齊入黎分享笑話","createTime":"2019-05-24T03:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:32:21.000Z","uid":1399,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae453dbaed6e604b1a8fec4b53ec675e63c96783","tid":1168843,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"一個神父很喜歡踢足球，不過他有個壞習慣，就是踢足球的時候常常會說粗口。<br />\n<br />\n有一天，他差一點就射中龍門，他說了一句：仆街！撻Q！<br />\n<br />\n突然天上傳來一把聲音：兒子啊！如果你再說粗口，我就用閃電劈你。<br />\n<br />\n神父聽了十分害怕，立即低頭懺悔，答應以後也不會再就粗口了。<br />\n<br />\n但本性難改，又有一天，神父空門前射失，他大叫了一聲：仆街! 撻Q！<br />\n<br />\n說時遲那時快天空立即雷電交加，神父心想這次死定了。<br />\n<br />\n閃電以極快的速度從天而落，把神父身邊的隊友劈死了。<br />\n<br />\n神父抬頭望天，百思不得其解之際．．．<br />\n天上傳來一把聲音: 仆街!撻Q!"},{"pid":"f384ca295434dc2da305e46e32bf6cc51fdeb22f","tid":1168843,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"e15549953afe5dfa09ab38c4b5cc8e0f708836d2","tid":1168843,"uid":241080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"還不錯"},{"pid":"99d1a74bafa45d343cac8db0ee45fa8ec7549aab","tid":1168843,"uid":1399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f384ca295434dc2da305e46e32bf6cc51fdeb22f","tid":1168843,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:22:40.000Z","msg":"你又唔係手足，死返出去啦"},{"pid":"629ca95a390fbbf87bdc7c9e4ecfaaaf7a641e03","tid":1168843,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59f20c6d005a9406e6f41e4cddfd3a9a9ddc5d0","tid":1168843,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:26:06.000Z","msg":"吊洗唔洗比負評比得咁快"},{"pid":"c8f64edfd1863b7245f8fbfdf9644b9e019e4a13","tid":1168843,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"